                <h3 class="bg-primary">Overview</h3>
                <p><strong>Hello Developers.</strong></p>
                <p>
                    The Don't Eat Alone API Platform can be used to build automated, authentic, high-quality apps and services that:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Help individuals share their own content with 3rd party apps.</li>
                    <li>Help developers generate content and build apps baced on our service</li>
